{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":544165,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"上一次内动荡恰好在31年前","timestamp":1605145557,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544183,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"唉那一代人的命运都要被彻底改变了","timestamp":1605145902,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544204,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 不，和平从来不是应该的，哪里来的\"改变\"？也许这正是我们的命运。","timestamp":1605146281,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544233,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 和平为什么不是应该的？战争就是因为你这种狂热战争贩子太多了","timestamp":1605146996,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544744,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 您去随便翻翻书，三十年的和平在历史上属于正常吗？","timestamp":1605152622,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544756,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 别告诉我与生俱来就是理所应当哈","timestamp":1605152800,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544783,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 在人类形成文明后出现频率原始社会＞封建＞资本主义，so应该退回到原始社会?","timestamp":1605153211,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544798,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"dave想说之前的历史中战争的确是主流，但和平才是趋势","timestamp":1605153498,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544811,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 30年确实很难得。这30年不仅做到了没有战争，还做到了版图稳定，经济发展。\n如果把条件放宽松一点，不考虑对越自卫反击和抗美援朝的话，甚至已经做到了70年的总体和平和版图稳定。70年这个成就应该没有哪个封建王朝做到了。","timestamp":1605153717,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544817,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 和平是趋势，但也不是应该的，是自己有力量才能得到的。要不然03年以前的伊拉克多繁荣，说没就没；79年的伊朗多繁荣，说没就没；79年的阿富汗多繁荣，至今还是蚂蚁窝...","timestamp":1605153874,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544825,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"倒也不是说什么应不应该，乐观点看，美国一百多年本土无战争，国内近三十年也还算平和，所以我还是相信和平会是人类社会的趋势。","timestamp":1605153986,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544827,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 不要只看失败者，看看战争的胜利者是何等繁荣","timestamp":1605153992,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544877,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 我说的是外无战争内无动荡，美国并不满足这两点。和平是人类社会的趋势这句话从积极人性的一面来讲没错，但问题是这个趋势在什么时候能达到什么样的状态？如果说不清楚这一点，这句话就不能够用来切实指导实践。","timestamp":1605154883,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544881,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 哪怕是资本主义能保证三十年的和平吗？","timestamp":1605154934,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":544941,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 瑞士，瑞典","timestamp":1605155935,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":545156,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 就那来个七块论？","timestamp":1605158896,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":545171,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 罗莎卢森堡女士在一百年前就说过：“要么社会主义，要么就野蛮人化”","timestamp":1605159219,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":545173,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 果然在中国人的正确的历史记忆里，九十年代转轨期大下岗导致的社会动荡是不存在的","timestamp":1605159291,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":545183,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 恰恰相反，反而是所谓的封建时代比起资本主义更和平！象征着资产阶级登上政治舞台的法国大革命之后，就是长达十多年的拿破仑战争。倒不如说随着资本主义在全球建立世界体系之后，整个世界无时无刻都有某一部分处在战争之中！","timestamp":1605159437,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":545227,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: 细说说？","timestamp":1605160105,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":546438,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":113434,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: 高姥爷最近都被喷自闭了 唉","timestamp":1605180489,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":113434,"reply":21,"tag":"政治相关","text":"#政治相关\n三十年外无战争内无动荡，真的太久了，久到让人错以为和平是理所应当的。\n然而我想我们这代人也许会和战争或者动荡一起度过自己生命中的壮年时光。","timestamp":1605145101,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782642,"url":"","vote":{}}}